"""
Step: 2.2
Name: ExtractQaManagerDocs
Inputs: 1_Inputs/speaker_data_*.parquet (2002-2018)
        1_Inputs/Unified-info.parquet
Outputs: 4_Outputs/2.2_ExtractQaManagerDocs/<timestamp>/qa_manager_docs_YYYY.parquet (17 files)
         4_Outputs/2.2_ExtractQaManagerDocs/<timestamp>/report_step_02.md
Logs: 3_Logs/2.2_ExtractQaManagerDocs/<timestamp>.log
Deterministic: True
Description: Extract QA-only managerial documents from earnings call transcripts

This script:
1. Loads all speaker_data parquet files (2002-2018)
2. Filters for Q&A context only (context == 'qa')
3. Applies managerial speaker filter (role keywords + employer matching)
4. Joins with Unified Info to get company_name
5. Concatenates speaker_text per file_name into single document
6. Outputs year-sharded parquet files (one per year)
7. Generates comprehensive report with filter statistics
"""

